12. Identify whether multiple findings should be corrected together.
13. Identify affected templates and system sheets.
14. Identify affected dashboard definitions, mappings, or validation rules.
15. Identify affected archives, indexes, hidden-sheet rules, and tab-order behavior.
16. Identify affected timing, audit, and diagnostic reports.
17. Identify expected failure modes if the finding remains unresolved.
18. Identify whether the correction changes approved business logic.

